reviewText: It was nice watching a older classic . it was the first adult movie I watched . loved every minute .there was nothing I didn't like

...in which Marilyn's character loses her virginity to GWA (gardener-with-attitude) David Morris appears as a part of Chapter 4. It's not a chapter of its own with a "thumbnail" identifying the link. That's the only problem with this DVD version--it doesn't take into accounting all the guys who have hunted down the poor-def clips people have bootlegged on YouTube and want a clearer version to watch on their Big Screen. It's obvious why--Marilyn was a lot younger in those days (only 27 or 28).
I have watched a small potion of Insatiable & it is just really nice. Compared to what they try to do today, well, Marilyn makes it feel comfortable, and easy on the eyes. Just a nice story.
